      <td><font face="Arial, helvetica" size="2">Permanent display of atmospheric pressure.
      When this option is not selected, atmospheric pressure is displayed during 5 s when push-button is pressed</font></td></tr>
  <tr><td><font face="Arial, helvetica" size="2"><center>Auto Reset</center></font></td>
      <td><font face="Arial, helvetica" size="2"><center>Menu 10</center></font></td>
      <td><font face="Arial, helvetica" size="2">Selection of automatic reset of altitude and event counter at ALTI-OSD power-up
 </font></td></tr>
